                            <comment id="51272" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Wed, 17 Feb 2010 08:16:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We are adding the missing varargs methods to JdbcTemplate for Spring 3.0.1 now, after already having generified much of JdbcTemplate in Spring 3.0 GA. However, we won&apos;t be deprecating SimpleJdbcTemplate at this point since it still combines JdbcTemplate and NamedParameterJdbcTemplate functionality into a single class with a &apos;simple&apos; selection of methods.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="51327" author="skaffman" created="Thu, 18 Feb 2010 21:28:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah, this is a dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6858&quot; title=&quot;Push the Java 5 simplifications in SimpleJdbcTemplate up to JdbcTemplate&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-6858&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-6858&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I see. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
